@startuml
title SDK Config Loader in Next.js (Before)
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #4E342E
skinparam defaultFontName Consolas

actor "Next.js Server Component" as NextServer #BBDEFB
component "@xylex-group/athena\ndist/index.js" as SdkBundle #FFE082
component "generator/config.ts\nloadGeneratorConfig()" as Loader #FFCCBC
component "direct dynamic import\nimport(`${moduleUrl.href}?cacheBust=...`)" as DynamicImport #EF9A9A
component "Webpack/Turbopack resolver" as Resolver #E1BEE7

NextServer --> SdkBundle : import createClient()/helpers
SdkBundle --> Loader : bundled export graph
Loader --> DynamicImport : parse import(expression)
Resolver --> DynamicImport : static resolution attempt
Resolver ..> NextServer : Module not found: Can't resolve <dynamic>

note right of DynamicImport
Bundler sees runtime template-string import
in a dependency bundle and aborts compile.
end note
@enduml